The paper deals with combinatorial and geometric aspects of sequences of points in the plane, and their monotonicity and convexity properties. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Discrete Mathematics (cs.DM), Computational Geometry (cs.CG), or Combinatorics and Discrete Mathematics (cs.CC) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper uses concepts from graph theory and Ramsey theory, which could place it in the Graph Theory (cs.GT) or Information Theory (cs.IT) sub-categories.
